Date: Mon, 8 Aug 2016 17:16:24 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Add debug flavour, remove lowlatency, signed-lowlatency and
 virtual

---
 meta-source/debian/control.d/debug             | 48 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 meta-source/debian/control.d/lowlatency        | 48 -----------------------
 meta-source/debian/control.d/signed-lowlatency | 19 ---------
 meta-source/debian/control.d/virtual           | 53 --------------------------
 4 files changed, 48 insertions(+), 120 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 meta-source/debian/control.d/debug
 delete mode 100644 meta-source/debian/control.d/lowlatency
 delete mode 100644 meta-source/debian/control.d/signed-lowlatency
 delete mode 100644 meta-source/debian/control.d/virtual

diff --git a/meta-source/debian/control.d/debug b/meta-source/debian/control.d/debug
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..d3f509f
--- /dev/null
+++ b/meta-source/debian/control.d/debug
@@ -0,0 +1,48 @@
+Package: linux-headers-debug@SUFFIX@
+Architecture: i386 amd64
+Section: devel
+Priority: optional
+Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-debug
+Description: debug Linux kernel headers
+ This package will always depend on the latest debug kernel headers
+ available.
+
+Package: linux-image-debug@SUFFIX@
+Architecture: i386 amd64
+Section: kernel
+Priority: optional
+Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-debug, linux-firmware
+Recommends: thermald [i386 amd64]
+Description: debug Linux kernel image
+ This package will always depend on the latest debug kernel image
+ available.
+
+Package: linux-tools-debug@SUFFIX@
+Architecture: i386 amd64
+Section: kernel
+Priority: optional
+Provides: linux-tools
+Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-tools-${kernel-abi-version}-debug
+Description: debug Linux kernel tools
+ This package will always depend on the latest debug kernel tools
+ available.
+
+Package: linux-cloud-tools-debug@SUFFIX@
+Architecture: i386 amd64
+Section: kernel
+Priority: optional
+Provides: linux-cloud-tools
+Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-cloud-tools-${kernel-abi-version}-debug
+Description: debug Linux kernel cloud tools
+ This package will always depend on the latest debug kernel cloud tools
+ available.
+
+Package: linux-debug@SUFFIX@
+Architecture: i386 amd64
+Section: kernel
+Priority: optional
+Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-debug@SUFFIX@ (= ${binary:Version}), linux-headers-debug@SUFFIX@ (= ${binary:Version})
+Description: Complete debug Linux kernel
+ This package will always depend on the latest complete debug Linux kernel
+ available.
+
